cuirassed.d:
a. Wearing a cuirass.
a. Having a covering of bony plates, resembling a cuirass;
   -- said of certain fishes.

currentness.d:
n. The quality of being current; currency; circulation;
   general reception.
n. Easiness of pronunciation; fluency.

curtana.d:
n. The pointless sword carried before English monarchs at
   their coronation, and emblematically considered as the sword of mercy;
   -- also called the sword of Edward the Confessor.
